peopleAlsoAsk.question: Are dept 56 houses hand painted?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: Each building and accessory is painted by hand according to specific direction from our artists. We fire our buildings and accessories a second time after painting to give more durability to the color finish.

peopleAlsoAsk.question: Can you mix Lemax and Department 56?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: I started with Lemax and now have some Dept 56 also. Dept 56 does scale larger so if you mix them you just have to be mindful of which pieces to put together. I include both on different levels to create perspective.
